  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"LASTORAGE\"</strong> is a warehouse work horror adventure where you must endure five days of eerie operations while navigating a strange and unsettling warehouse world.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >As the sole employee of this warehouse, you have been welcomed by the owner and assigned five days of tasks.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Complete Your Duties</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must open packages, inspect their contents, and transport goods. However, some inspection criteria are inexplicably strange, and the packages may contain clearly unnatural foreign objects...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.poster.avif?t=1743478081\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.webm?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.mp4?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stay Alert</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind these simple tasks, many strange entities are lurking. Stay alert, look around carefully, and avoid being caught off guard.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.poster.avif?t=1743478081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.webm?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.mp4?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover the Truth of the Warehouse</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The secret behind this eerie warehouse lies beyond the pitch-black gate. Face the unknown and uncover the mysteries hidden within this unsettling world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Elements</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number of endings: 2</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A custom mode where you can freely play only the tasks (includes all content from DAY 1 to DAY 5).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Estimated playtime</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 to 2 hours</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"LASTORAGE\"</strong> is a warehouse work horror adventure where you must endure five days of eerie operations while navigating a strange and unsettling warehouse world.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >As the sole employee of this warehouse, you have been welcomed by the owner and assigned five days of tasks.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Complete Your Duties</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must open packages, inspect their contents, and transport goods. However, some inspection criteria are inexplicably strange, and the packages may contain clearly unnatural foreign objects...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.poster.avif?t=1743478081\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.webm?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/e11784d79456614239720982abb09514.mp4?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stay Alert</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind these simple tasks, many strange entities are lurking. Stay alert, look around carefully, and avoid being caught off guard.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.poster.avif?t=1743478081\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.webm?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552510/extras/341634858a1431839e3730569b926716.mp4?t=1743478081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover the Truth of the Warehouse</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The secret behind this eerie warehouse lies beyond the pitch-black gate. Face the unknown and uncover the mysteries hidden within this unsettling world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Elements</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number of endings: 2</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A custom mode where you can freely play only the tasks (includes all content from DAY 1 to DAY 5).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Estimated playtime</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 to 2 hours</p></li></ul>",
